Package org.gicentre.utils.io Description

File input/output utilities for use with Processing.

This package includes classes for handling file input/output, for example an XML reader and writer.

To check you have the latest version of the gicentreUtils package, display the results of Version.getText() or Version.getVersion(). It should match that shown in this API documentation.
